ContainedObjects.Name: Custom_Model
ContainedObjects.LuaScript:
function onCollisionEnter(collision_info)
  if(self.is_face_down)then
    self.setName('Negative Red Potion')
  else
    self.setName('Positive Red Potion')
  end
end
